WEBVTT

00:02.470 --> 00:03.502
Louis: Oh, what's going on
in my house?

00:03.504 --> 00:05.437
Is it a birthday party?

00:05.439 --> 00:07.106
[ Chuckles ] Oh.
There he...

00:07.108 --> 00:09.341
Uh, ma.

00:09.343 --> 00:11.977
There he is...
The birthday boy!

00:11.979 --> 00:14.947
Mom, this isn't
a "star wars" cake.

00:14.949 --> 00:16.682
Yes, it is.

00:16.684 --> 00:18.684
That's the "star wars" bear.

00:18.686 --> 00:20.986
What? No.
You mean Chewbacca?

00:20.988 --> 00:22.488
No, no, that's not a good name.

00:22.490 --> 00:25.858
That's...
It's too Greek.

00:25.860 --> 00:27.626
You know, I knew
a Greek bear once.

00:27.628 --> 00:31.030
You're right, Louis.
I am good at throwing parties.

00:31.032 --> 00:32.998
Uh, I didn't say
anything...
look at the piñata.

00:33.000 --> 00:34.333
It's in great shape.

00:34.335 --> 00:37.302
No one can tell we've used it
since Eddie was 2.

00:37.304 --> 00:39.204
This year,
I filled it with cereal.

00:39.206 --> 00:40.005
[ Tape ripping ]

00:40.007 --> 00:42.007
Oh. Uh-oh.

00:42.009 --> 00:43.575
No, ma, get...

00:43.577 --> 00:45.844
Hey, boys, say hi to...

00:45.846 --> 00:47.713
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

00:47.715 --> 00:50.082
