did you guys use?

00:50.084 --> 00:51.383
The perfect amount.

00:51.385 --> 00:53.419
I don't like it
when the ends get bunchy.

00:53.421 --> 00:54.720
We got him pogs.

00:54.722 --> 00:56.055
I told you all about them

00:56.057 --> 00:57.723
when we were getting
our hair cut, remember?

00:57.725 --> 00:59.158
Uh, mm-hmm.

00:59.160 --> 01:01.560
Hey.
Okay, no light swords
in the house!

01:01.562 --> 01:02.895
Ow!
[ Body thuds ]

01:02.897 --> 01:04.396
Oh, my goodness!
Louis!
Oh. [ Groans ]

01:04.398 --> 01:05.898
Is the camera okay?

01:05.900 --> 01:07.366
I fell on a hot wheel.

01:07.368 --> 01:09.668
Eddie: Before we start yelling,
just remember,

01:09.670 --> 01:12.438
the force works
in mysterious ways.

01:12.440 --> 01:14.440
Ma!

01:14.442 --> 01:16.775
