to have it with us.

08:38.819 --> 08:41.219
You're embarrassed of us,
you and Mitch.

08:41.221 --> 08:42.787
I'm not embarrassed!

08:42.789 --> 08:45.624
We would have been happy
to host your friends here.

08:45.626 --> 08:47.292
It's just different
when you're around.

08:47.294 --> 08:49.027
Oh, but not when Mitch
is around?

08:49.029 --> 08:51.029
Enough with Mitch.
It's getting weird.

08:51.031 --> 08:52.664
I just wanted
to spend my birthday

08:52.666 --> 08:54.106
with people
who I can be myself with.

08:55.469 --> 08:57.369
What are you talking about?

08:57.371 --> 08:59.070
You're yourself with us,

08:59.072 --> 09:00.805
with the rap music
and the sleeping.

09:00.807 --> 09:01.840
See?

09:01.842 --> 09:03.241
You guys have this idea of me,

09:03.243 --> 09:04.743
but I'm more than just that.

09:04.745 --> 09:07.646
Well, how are you different
around your friends?

09:07.648 --> 09:09.681
I don't know.
I'm just different.

09:09.683 --> 09:14.085
I'm, like, smart
and funny and athletic and...

09:14.087 --> 09:15.720
And generous!

09:15.722 --> 09:19.758
Well, I would love to know
smart, sporty, hilarious Eddie.

09:19.760 --> 09:21.259
Be that way at home, then!

09:21.261 --> 09:22.994
I can't.

09:22.996 --> 09:25.363
There's so many rules
around here, I can never relax!

09:25.365 --> 09:29.000
Do the dishes, turn your music
down, don't own a lizard!

09:29.002 --> 09:31.002
I'm never gonna be good enough
like Emery and Evan.

09:31.772 --> 09:35.106
Just...

09:35.108 --> 09:37.242
