Would a good kid do this?

09:53.126 --> 09:54.459
Shirt boobs.

09:56.063 --> 10:00.498
Hello? React!
This is not okay!

10:05.572 --> 10:07.539
You think Eddie's right,
don't you?

10:07.541 --> 10:09.240
You think we're too strict.

10:09.242 --> 10:11.409
I think we're good parents.

10:11.411 --> 10:12.944
But he's getting older,

10:12.946 --> 10:15.914
and I think it wouldn't hurt
to relax our rules a little.

10:15.916 --> 10:17.549
Our rules are there
for a reason.

10:17.551 --> 10:18.917
It's our job to protect him.

10:18.919 --> 10:21.786
But if we keep trying to control
everything he does,

10:21.788 --> 10:23.254
we're going to drive him away.

10:23.256 --> 10:26.091
This is the only way
I know how to be.

10:26.093 --> 10:29.628
Well, you can still be you,
just... A little less.

10:31.264 --> 10:32.731
Look, if we don't adjust,

10:32.733 --> 10:34.399
he won't want
to spend any days with us,

10:34.401 --> 10:35.667
let alone his birthday.

10:35.669 --> 10:37.135
[ Sighs ]

10:37.137 --> 10:39.337
I liked you better when
you were worried about Mitch.

10:39.339 --> 10:41.940
