13:11.424 --> 13:12.590
Jessica.

13:12.592 --> 13:13.892
Fine.

13:13.894 --> 13:15.960
You can sleep over at Dave's.

13:15.962 --> 13:17.162
But I'm coming, too.

13:17.164 --> 13:18.730
Jessica.
Fine.

13:18.732 --> 13:21.800
I will just stand outside
and look in the window.

13:21.802 --> 13:25.737
Jessica.
<i>Louis.</i>

13:25.739 --> 13:28.039
¶¶

13:33.180 --> 13:34.479
Have fun at the sleepover.

13:34.481 --> 13:35.914
I will.

13:35.916 --> 13:36.981
You remembered your toothbrush?

13:36.983 --> 13:39.083
Yes, I remembered my toothbrush.

13:39.085 --> 13:41.085
I packed you a snack.

13:41.087 --> 13:42.954
There's gonna be food there,
mom.

13:42.956 --> 13:44.622
Keep your sneakers close to you.

13:44.624 --> 13:46.457
If you sense any danger,
you run.

13:46.459 --> 13:48.326
You run right back here to me.

13:48.328 --> 13:49.761
He'll just be three houses down.

13:49.763 --> 13:51.329
He's gonna be fine.

13:51.331 --> 13:52.497
Have a great time, son.

13:52.499 --> 13:54.666
I will.

13:54.668 --> 13:56.367
See ya!

13:56.369 --> 14:00.638
¶¶

14:00.640 --> 14:02.340
How long
are you gonna do that for?

14:02.342 --> 14:06.144
Until he comes home.

14:06.146 --> 14:11.482
[ Doorbell rings,
knock on door ]

14:11.484 --> 14:12.817
Hey, dude.
Come on in.

14:12.819 --> 14:14.319
I just cracked you a cold one.

14:14.321 --> 14:16.321
Nice!
Can I get a cup?

14:16.323 --> 14:18.003
You've got one.
It's attached to your face.

14:22.062 --> 14:24.462
Uh-huh. Uh-huh.

14:24.464 --> 14:25.496
Yeah.

14:25.498 --> 14:26.998
Dude, my mom doesn't care.
She's cool.

14:27.000 --> 14:30.134
Yes, yes.
He just got here, Jessica.

14:30.136 --> 14:31.502
Jessica:
Are you looking at him?

14:31.504 --> 14:33.071
Yes, I'm looking at him
right now.

14:33.073 --> 14:34.672
He needs vitamins before bed.

14:34.674 --> 14:36.074
Okay.
Watch him take them.

14:36.076 --> 14:38.243
I'll be sure he takes
his vitamins before bed.

14:38.245 --> 14:39.677
He'll try to put them
under his...
okay, bye!

14:39.679 --> 14:41.079
[ Telephone beeps ]
[ Chuckles ]
don't worry.

14:41.081 --> 14:42.513
I'm not gonna make you do that.

14:42.515 --> 14:44.549
Wow.
Thanks, Mrs. Selby.

14:44.551 --> 14:45.817
[ Dog barks ]

14:45.819 --> 14:47.652
You have a dog?!

14:47.654 --> 14:49.721
Yeah, my mom just found him
on the bus.

14:49.723 --> 14:50.989
We named him banjo.

14:50.991 --> 14:53.057
After the best instrument.

14:53.059 --> 14:55.193
How about this instrument?

14:55.195 --> 14:56.461
[ Burps loudly ]

15:00.233 --> 15:02.734
Yes!

15:02.736 --> 15:06.504
Nice one! Mm!
Hoo-hoo!

15:09.342 --> 15:11.843
If this doesn't get
their attention, nothing will.

15:11.845 --> 15:14.279
Once we run away,
they'll really be sorry.

15:14.281 --> 15:15.513
We'll get so far
from this place,

15:15.515 --> 15:16.748
they'll never be able
to find us.

15:16.750 --> 15:18.549
Let's go to Denver.

15:18.551 --> 15:21.252
I heard their cheesesteaks
are amazing.
Huh.

15:26.092 --> 15:27.859
Jessica, it's not a good time.

15:27.861 --> 15:29.594
There's been a death
in the family.

15:29.596 --> 15:32.397
I won't disturb you.
Take all the time you need.

15:32.399 --> 15:34.465
I just want to see
if I could see my son

15:34.467 --> 15:36.367
at Dave's house
through your living-room window.

15:40.473 --> 15:41.806
Oh, that's terrible.

15:41.808 --> 15:44.242
That's...
That's terrible.

15:44.244 --> 15:46.711
How's Barb?
Is she holding up?

15:46.713 --> 15:48.279
Honey, do you have a stool?

15:48.281 --> 15:49.580
Uh...

15:49.582 --> 15:52.617
Uh-huh.

15:52.619 --> 15:53.885
No.

15:53.887 --> 15:58.589
No, don't say that.
He loved you very much.

15:58.591 --> 15:59.958
Don't beat yourself up.

15:59.960 --> 16:02.760
Is my wife here?

16:02.762 --> 16:05.296
Honey, do you have
any barbecue chips?

16:07.767 --> 16:09.400
Jessica, what are you doing?

16:09.402 --> 16:11.402
You were going to loosen
the reins, remember?

16:11.404 --> 16:13.271
I'm just making sure he's okay.

16:13.273 --> 16:14.806
He's never gonna know.

16:14.808 --> 16:16.908
Uh-huh. Yes.

16:16.910 --> 16:18.977
Yeah, we can definitely pick sue
and Donna up from the airport.

16:18.979 --> 16:20.178
Whatever's easiest for you.

16:21.247 --> 16:23.448
Eclipse! [ Gasps ]

16:23.450 --> 16:26.017
Oh.

16:26.019 --> 16:27.019
Oh.

16:29.823 --> 16:32.123
Light swords in the house.

16:32.125 --> 16:34.092
Looks like he's having fun.

16:34.094 --> 16:36.361
Well, that's good, right?
That's what we wanted.

16:36.363 --> 16:38.629
Right.

16:38.631 --> 16:41.466
Hey. [ Chuckles ]
I'm sorry I'm late.

16:41.468 --> 16:44.535
I knocked back
a few too many vodka lemonades.

16:44.537 --> 16:45.837
[ Giggles ]

16:45.839 --> 16:47.572
Your brother's dead.

16:49.709 --> 16:51.042
And the huangs are here.

16:54.214 --> 16:55.847
[ Video game music playing ]

16:55.849 --> 16:57.849
[<i> Grunting</i> ]

16:57.851 --> 16:59.384
<i>End it.</i>

16:59.386 --> 17:00.651
[ Sighs ]

17:00.653 --> 17:01.953
<i>Fatality.</i>

17:01.955 --> 17:04.188
Dude, you just ripped my spine
out of my back.

17:04.190 --> 17:06.791
Watch. I'm gonna play it
like a saxophone.

17:06.793 --> 17:08.659
[<i> Saxophone plays</i> ]

17:08.661 --> 17:10.795
I'd never be able
to play this game at home.

17:10.797 --> 17:12.163
Okay, fellas, pause the game.

17:12.165 --> 17:13.731
Pause, pause, pause.
Who's hungry?

17:13.733 --> 17:15.233
Whoa.

17:15.235 --> 17:17.368
That cereal is made
of little cookies!

17:17.370 --> 17:19.904
But wait. Aren't we
gonna spoil our dinner?

17:19.906 --> 17:20.972
Dude, this<i> is</i> our dinner.

17:22.075 --> 17:24.409
I love the way you live.

17:24.411 --> 17:25.877
Thanks, mom.
You're welcome.

17:25.879 --> 17:27.178
Here's your tip.
[ Farts ]

17:27.180 --> 17:29.547
Oh! [ Laughs ]
You got me!

17:29.549 --> 17:31.849
27-25, you!

17:31.851 --> 17:33.584
[ Gasps, laughs ]

17:33.586 --> 17:35.953
Not for long, though.
Mama's got one brewing.

17:37.924 --> 17:40.691
O-Kay.

17:40.693 --> 17:43.294
¶¶

17:47.000 --> 17:48.833
[ clattering ]

17:48.835 --> 17:49.834
[ Dog barking in distance ]

17:49.836 --> 17:51.602
Head back in?

17:51.604 --> 17:53.004
Yep.

17:56.609 --> 17:57.241
Mm.

17:57.243 --> 17:59.410
Dog hair everywhere.

17:59.412 --> 18:02.146
So soft, right?
It's banjo's belly hair.

18:04.918 --> 18:07.251
Dude, you're getting ice cream
on my pillow!

18:07.253 --> 18:08.686
Just rub it in.

18:08.688 --> 18:10.121
[ Scoffs ]

18:16.563 --> 18:18.763
Bro, it's, like, midnight.

18:18.765 --> 18:20.565
And my stomach's still shredded

18:20.567 --> 18:22.100
from all
that tiny cookie cereal.

18:22.102 --> 18:24.068
[ Knock on door ]

18:24.070 --> 18:27.305
Lights out, boys.
Time for bed.
Okay.

18:27.307 --> 18:28.906
I don't want
to go to bed!
Go to bed, damn it!

18:28.908 --> 18:30.641
I hate you!
I hate you back!

18:30.643 --> 18:32.310
I wish you were dead!

18:32.312 --> 18:34.579
Oh, put it on
your Christmas wish list!

18:34.581 --> 18:37.482
Ugh!

18:37.484 --> 18:39.250
That was intense.

18:39.252 --> 18:41.786
Ah, we do that every night.
No big deal.

18:41.788 --> 18:43.788
Now she's gonna go put on
some Whitney Houston,

18:43.790 --> 18:45.823
dance alone in her room
for an hour, then go to bed.

18:45.825 --> 18:48.493
If I talked to my mom that way,
she'd kill me.

18:48.495 --> 18:51.062
Really?
Yeah.

18:51.064 --> 18:53.731
Like, I'd be like,
"I don't want to,"

18:53.733 --> 18:55.766
and then I would be killed.

18:55.768 --> 18:58.269
Well, it<i> is</i> pretty weird
in your house.

18:58.271 --> 18:59.437
What do you mean?

18:59.439 --> 19:01.606
Well, there's so many rules
over there.

19:01.608 --> 19:03.741
You have to eat dinner
at the table every night,

19:03.743 --> 19:06.444
you have to do your chores,
you can't have a lizard.

19:06.446 --> 19:09.113
That's not weird.
<i>Your</i> house is weird.

19:09.115 --> 19:10.448
What's weird about my house?

19:10.450 --> 19:13.184
Dude, you fart on your mom!

19:13.186 --> 19:15.520
Whatever.

19:15.522 --> 19:17.488
Night, man.

19:19.425 --> 19:21.492
[ Sighs ]

19:21.494 --> 19:24.762
¶ I get so emotional, baby ¶

19:24.764 --> 19:25.930
Christa: Whoo!

19:25.932 --> 19:28.499
¶ Every time I think of you ¶

19:28.501 --> 19:29.634
[ exhales deeply ]

19:29.636 --> 19:31.169
¶ I get so emo... ¶

19:33.473 --> 19:34.572
[ knock on door ]

19:37.310 --> 19:38.442
Eddie? [ Gasps ]

19:38.444 --> 19:39.844
Louis, wake up!
Eddie's home!

19:39.846 --> 19:42.146
I'm awake.
Everything all right?

19:42.148 --> 19:44.215
Yeah, it's fine.
I don't know.

19:44.217 --> 19:46.551
I just wanted to come home.
Is that okay?

19:46.553 --> 19:50.221
Of course it is.
I'm just surprised.

19:50.223 --> 19:51.823
I-I thought
you would have fun at Dave's.

19:51.824 --> 19:55.293
I did.
And then... I didn't.

19:55.295 --> 19:57.895
[ Sighs ]
I like being with my friends,

19:57.897 --> 20:01.365
but I like being at home, too.

20:01.367 --> 20:03.301
Do you want me
to make you birthday noodles?

20:03.303 --> 20:05.403
Sure.

20:05.405 --> 20:07.905
Doesn't that take
like six hours?

20:07.907 --> 20:11.876
It is for my son.

20:14.847 --> 20:17.081
Emery: Are those
Eddie's birthday noodles?

20:17.083 --> 20:19.884
But it's not even
his birthday anymore.

20:19.886 --> 20:21.485
What are you doing up so late?

20:21.487 --> 20:24.589
It's way past your bedtime.
You two are grounded.

20:26.192 --> 20:27.992
Both: Yay!

20:27.994 --> 20:29.894
Wait.
Where are you going?

20:29.896 --> 20:32.330
It took me six hours
to make these noodles.

20:32.332 --> 20:33.831
Noodles, then bed,
then grounded.

20:37.170 --> 20:39.503
Eddie: I don't know
what I missed more...

20:39.505 --> 20:42.206
Your noodles or your rules.

20:42.208 --> 20:44.275
Chew with your mouth closed.

20:44.277 --> 20:47.111
Noodles, definitely.

20:52.518 --> 20:55.119
So I said, "ma'am, you can stay",

20:55.121 --> 20:57.054
but your dog's
got to go."

20:57.056 --> 20:59.423
[ Both laugh ]

20:59.425 --> 21:01.125
When did you guys
become friends?

21:01.127 --> 21:02.426
What?

21:02.428 --> 21:04.195
Well, we were in the service
together.

21:04.197 --> 21:05.930
What are you talking about?

21:05.932 --> 21:07.531
The table service.

21:07.533 --> 21:09.634
You know, during
the fajita craze?

21:09.636 --> 21:12.937
Once a fajita man,
always a fajita man.

21:12.939 --> 21:15.239
[ Both imitate sizzling ]

21:15.241 --> 21:16.907
See this?

21:16.909 --> 21:19.110
Shrimp jumped off a skillet,
got me right here.

21:19.112 --> 21:20.711
That's nothing.

21:20.713 --> 21:22.947
Chicken/beef combo, extra oil.

21:22.949 --> 21:25.950
Uh, look at this scar.

21:25.952 --> 21:28.386
An old man with dementia
stabbed me on the street.
